description: Here it is, my first NFT. A shot of a giraffe in the rain, a recent photo that's become one of my favourites so far. This will be a one of one in this form (there will be some variations down the track, however this will be the only one featuring solely the original photo). No commercial rights are given but you have unlimited personal use. Thankyou to everyone, your interest and support has been invaluable!!
